{
  "stem": "25027.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They thought we were with the-- with the underground, with the Israeli underground.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we explained to them that we were survivors, and we lost our family.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were looking for, you know-- they had a translator, a Polish translator.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think the Polish guy went to the British to tell them about us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And after we saw what was going on there, we also saw part of the Jewish Brigade was there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After a day or two we decided we didn't want to stay in the British zone, and we went back to Stuttgart in the American zone.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Stuttgart.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The UNRRA was there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The United Nations Relief Organization.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And the HIAS was already connected with the UNRRA to help-- you know what the HIAS is-- to help Jewish survivors.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I registered my name to see also-- and I was looking at their listings-- if anybody in my family maybe was registered, or-- nobody.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They told-- they asked me could I drive a vehicle?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said yes, I could drive a Studebaker truck.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They gave me the Studebaker truck, and I was bringing in supplies to the Jewish camp, which was in the city of Stuttgart, part of the city.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Most camps were usually on the outside.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was-- what the French did, actually, when they liberated the city of Stuttgart, they took the Jews out of the camp, they evacuated all the Germans from a two or three block area, and they gave these apartment houses to the Jews.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Those were the good French.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was part of that group of displaced persons.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
